Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Upper Yard" "Angel Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God's Island, Upper Yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the ruins that spread around Giant Jack,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,men clashed against one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As this fierce battle for survival rages on,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki, a female Shandian warrior,\Nfalls at the hands of God Eneru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Nami, Gan Fall and Aisa,\Nwho were swallowed by the giant snake,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,met someone they never\Nexpected to see in its stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bursting Slash! Zoro vs. Ohm!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! The one I have to beat first is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it wasn't enough!\NThen I'll just keep trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! That extendable sword\Nthis priest uses is a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that snake is the one I have to beat first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get Nami and the\Nweird knight out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they were swallowed whole,\Nso they probably didn't die outright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just a matter of time before they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard... Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape my attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:04:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just as no one can ever\Nescape the reality of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I'm just wasting my breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you probably don't have enough\Nsense to realize you're about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realize your foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a small being who is very anxious\Nabout the gold before your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cannot see your inalterable fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where the heck is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where will he attack from next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!\NWhy does he know where I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if he can see me from behind the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is that horn-shaped\Nsunglass-wearing freak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Blue Sea person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no business with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another voice has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The survivors in the Upper Ruins are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...five people... and two animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself, Ohm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's four people and two animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hawk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! An iron wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword is Iron Clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think clouds have a set shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Fork!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Fleuret!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! I can't avoid it! Why is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's reading my movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You depend on your swords,\Nso keeping a distance does you no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-six Caliber Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisen Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be repelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite an interesting\Ntechnique, Blue Sea person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you going to try that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you lose sight of me,\NI can know exactly where you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by using Mantra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shandian warriors aren't\Nintimidated by a mere dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there're three people\Nand two animals left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...although it'll soon be\Ntwo people and two animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you're the axis\Nof the Blue Sea people group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and your comrades all fought well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I've already taken aim at your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pray to God, swordsman from the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! I'll never pray to God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difference among people\Nis if they die sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do want you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of your arrogant lecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I can't see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that extendable sword of yours\Nwill tell me where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! The moment you find out\Nwill be the moment you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past held 36 worldly desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The present holds 72 worldly desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future will hold 108 worldly desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style!\NOne-hundred-eight Caliber Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The iron clouds were repelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww! Eww! Eww! Eww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dead end!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Balloon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... This mystery cave is a horrible cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, this isn't a cave!\NWe're inside the snake's stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami, you're okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami! Hang in there! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Are you gonna\Nsqueeze me to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you doing, Aisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our enemy! An enemy who\Ntook away the Shandians' homeland!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of taking the\Nhead of the weird knight here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before Eneru showed up, he was\Nthe leader of the Skypieans!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Skypieans, who drove us\NShandians out of our homeland!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was 400 long years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't him who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your people would be satisfied by\Ntaking my head, I'd gladly give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the way things are now, taking my\Nhead alone wouldn't settle things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the hostility between the Shandians\Nand Skypieans does not change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ancestors took your homeland\Naway from you, Shandians.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot find a way to\Napologize for that action.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes by while I\Ncontinue to remain helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I would like\Nto apologize one by one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:45.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Knight"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to all Shandians who died in seeking\Ntheir homeland in the past 400 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:13:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sincerely sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weird knight has been trying very hard\Nso that everyone that lives in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can get along and live peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, if you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get along and live peacefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's bad is when one race\Nrefuses to coexist with another!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why did you stop me?! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's apologizing, so there's no\Nneed to take his life, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold, Shandora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden bell that must've been in the\Ncenter of the city isn't here any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The belfry for that bell might've\Nhad Poneglyphs engraved on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this city fell in order to protect\Nthe Poneglyphs, as I suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it should still be hidden\Nsomewhere even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The belfry with the\NPoneglyphs engraved on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, where could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? This is... a rail for lorries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something was taken out from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still new... I wonder what was taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing? Even after\Nbeing shot up to the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this city, Shandora,\Nstill majestically exists like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's a legendary city,\Nif it's covered by clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can't even show off its figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those stupid former Gods\Ndidn't even notice this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you're an\Narchaeologist from the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took even us several\Nmonths to find these ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can read the letters on the ruins,\Nyou can find this place that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the gold you're\Nlooking for isn't here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a few years late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I can't find any.\NIt must be you who took it out from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold is a nice thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That glittering metal suits me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you took the golden bell\Nthat used to be here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's interesting. What did you\Nlearn by reading the letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Unfortunately, if it wasn't\Nhere when you first came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it didn't come to the sky after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The huge golden bell that\NShandora took pride in,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the large belfry for that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to see the belfry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait... Yes! It's here. It's here in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this island was blown\Ninto the sky 400 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, on the day that\NGod's Island, Upper Yard, was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's said that the loud chimes of a bell\Nrang throughout the entire nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...although old people in this nation\Ncall it the island's singing voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.73,0:17:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That bell was made of gold! Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon the game will be over.\NEight more minutes to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, why don't I\Nlook for... the golden bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden bell is in the sky?\NThen... Poneglyphs, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's a maggot\Nat the edge of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hang in there, Usopp-san, Sanji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They still haven't awoken yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But they'll definitely get well, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure will. There's no way that\Nsuch kind people won't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is that,\Nwhen the sky becomes peaceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to once again show everyone\Nhospitality to my heart's content...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Suu?!\NIs it time for your meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suu, what's wrong? Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be that you're...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of those who fought\Nwith Gan Fall-sama six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as I thought, you're a\Nmember of the Divine Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a closed-off area, we were...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-san, attend to him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, Father!\N--Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife and children are on Angel Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everyone's worried about you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let everyone know!\NEneru is planning to return everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skypiea will be dropped to the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This nation will disappear!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time to lose!\NTell them right away! Eneru is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...planning to eliminate\Neveryone living in the sky!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate everyone from the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second, please!\NIf he does such a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there won't be a place\Neven for God Eneru himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got an ark! "Ark Maxim"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ark... Maxim?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:21:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were forced to spend the last\Nsix years building that flying ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is that,\Nwhen the sky becomes peaceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to once again show everyone\Nhospitality to my heart's content...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Racing full speed ahead as always
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A to Z, we run through it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all have worries and fall many times
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we just need to rise to the top someday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:22:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could be beyond the sea\Nin which the morning sun rises?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go little by little toward\Nthe brilliantly shining sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never treat you "bad"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times did we fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, we're definitely\Npointing at tomorrow now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile! Come back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to you, friends\NCome back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to you, friends\NCome back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to you, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is approaching.\NI'll put an end to the survival game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! The ground broke into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.39,0:23:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this our homeland, the one we've\Nbeen fighting for for 400 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems there's an extra person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Collapsing Upper Ruins!\NThe Quintet for the Finale!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
